('11554ced-9183-4bd2-b314-8e0969a68a21', 'Lasagna', 'Pasta', 'capiche', null, null, null, 7, 'approved', 143.63, 143.63, 740, 0, 5, false, 1300, 'Gram', 1, ARRAY['Heat oil in a pan; sauté onion, carrot, celery and garlic until soft.','Add soaked and drained soy chunks; cook for 3–4 min.','Add tomato passata, tomato paste, oregano, salt and pepper. Simmer 15–20 min.','Make béchamel: melt butter, add flour; cook 1 min. Gradually whisk in milk. Cook until thick. Season with salt and nutmeg.','In a baking dish, layer: bolognese sauce, sheets, béchamel, mozzarella. Repeat layers. Top with parmesan.','Bake at 180°C for 40–45 min or until golden and bubbling. Rest 10 min before serving.']::text[], null, null, '2026-06-20T09:30:00.000Z', null, '2026-06-01T09:00:00.000Z', '2026-06-01T09:00:00.000Z'),
